First grind the oreo cookies finely in a mixer.
Then take it out in a bowl, mix with milk and make a smooth batter.
Pour the batter into a new bowl.
Put the bowl in a microwave for 20 to 25 minutes
Then take the bowl out by a cloth or gloves.(be careful)
Keep in room temperature for 10 to 15 minutes.
Decorate the cake with the chocolate syrup on it.(optional)
Your oreo cake is ready!